719703f-b.title: Manhattan: Exchange Place - New Street
719703f-b.text:
(1)
Exchange Place, north side, from New, to Broad Streets. Iu the
foreground, appears the excavation on the site of the former
Johnstone Building, at No. 30 Broad Street.
September 16, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a different angle. Building standing between
excavations, is the Ocean Cable Offices, at No. 38-4O Broad Street.
September 16, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
